@dev Query total supply of token
 @return Total supply of token

@dev Creates `amount` tokens and assigns them to `account`, increasing
 the total supply.
 Emits a {Transfer} event with `from` set to the zero address.
 Requirements:
 - `account` cannot be the zero address.

@dev Query total supply of token
 @return Total supply of token

@dev Creates `amount` tokens and assigns them to `account`, increasing
 the total supply.
 Emits a {Transfer} event with `from` set to the zero address.
 Requirements:
 - `account` cannot be the zero address.

params._owner: The address of the account owning tokens
params._spender: The address of the account able to transfer the tokens

returns._0: Amount of remaining tokens allowed to spent

params._spender: The address of the account able to transfer the tokens
params._value: The amount of wei to be approved for transfer
